Bloomberg's  Erik Schatzker , Scarlet 
Fu and Sara Eisen report on a phone sting, known as Operation 
Honey Stick, operated by Symantec to track information accessed 
on lost or stolen smartphones from a story in this week's issue 
of Bloomberg Businessweek. They speak on Bloomberg Television's 
"Inside Track."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 03:02
 